 class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 28, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mco1764050915461.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mco1764050915461.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mco1764050915461.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mco1764050915461\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The observability feature in Uniface offers insights into your application's internal\n\t\tstate by analyzing telemetry data. It enables you to monitor performance, troubleshoot\n\t\tissues, and optimize your application for reliability and scalability.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Observability in Uniface is based on the <strong class=\"ph b\">OpenTelemetry (OTel)</strong> standard, ensuring\n\t\t\tcompatibility with popular tools such as Jaeger, Tempo, Loki, and ELK. This feature\n\t\t\tenables the collection of observability data without requiring changes to existing\n\t\t\tUniface applications. To begin generating telemetry, activate the required configuration\n\t\t\tsettings.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mco1764050915461__section_gsz_wfr_khc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d309788e55\">Supported Telemetry Types</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"mco1764050915461__ul_e5j_yfr_khc\">\n<li class=\"li\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Traces</strong><p class=\"p\">Uniface generates trace data for each ProcScript module,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tshowing the flow of ProcScript execution through your application. This\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thelps identify bottlenecks and latency issues.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Logs</strong><p class=\"p\">All <a class=\"xref\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rlu1665702707277.html\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">putmess</a> logs within your\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tapplication can be exported as timestamped OpenTelemetry logs, useful\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tfor debugging and root cause analysis.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mco1764050915461__section_fgq_pgr_khc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d309788e83\">Supported Platforms</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">For details of the platforms that Uniface observability supports, see <a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://community.rocketsoftware.com/rocket-uniface-product-updates-108/uniface-product-availability-information-18191\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Platform Availability Matrix</a>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_24137425\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_24137425\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Observability Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 28, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The observability feature in Uniface offers insights into your application's internal state by analyzing telemetry data. It enables you to monitor performance, troubleshoot issues, and optimize your application for reliability and scalability. Observability in Uniface is based on the OpenTelemetry (OTel) standard, ensuring compatibility with popular tools such as Jaeger, Tempo, Loki, and ELK. This feature enables the collection of observability data without requiring changes to existing Uniface applications. To begin generating telemetry, activate the required configuration settings. Supported Telemetry Types Traces Uniface generates trace data for each ProcScript module, showing the flow of ProcScript execution through your application. This helps identify bottlenecks and latency issues. Logs All putmess logs within your application can be exported as timestamped OpenTelemetry logs, useful for debugging and root cause analysis. Supported Platforms For details of the platforms that Uniface observability supports, see Platform Availability Matrix . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}